{"tid":541662,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前曼聯助教：連格就是『英格蘭恩尼斯達』","createTime":"2018-01-26T16:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T09:07:32.000Z","uid":56810,"like":32,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"30f3db34aa5a0e69db6337251aa2141e05af52a2","tid":541662,"uid":56810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:25:44.000Z","msg":"曼聯中場連格今季奠定了正選席位，今季英超上陣20場轟入7球，表現令人眼前一亮。前曼聯助教梅倫史甸（Rene Meulensteen）最近披露，雲尼斯達羅以及科蘭都當年都對連格讚譽有加，又形容對方是「英格蘭恩尼斯達」！<br />\n<br />\n對於連格當年還在青年軍受訓的情形，梅倫史甸說：「這令我想起雲尼斯達羅以及科蘭當時來觀看訓練的情形，當他們見到連格時都異口同聲說『天呀！這孩子好出色！』」<br />\n<br />\n梅倫史甸又拿巴塞球星恩尼斯達與連格比較：「我從他們的比賽中看到，兩人的打法好多相似的地方。我相信連格就是『英格蘭恩尼斯達』。我覺得你可以叫他加盟巴塞，然後打恩尼斯達的位置，他一定能夠勝任。他在英超能夠做到，而英超比西甲難打，絕對要看高一線。」"},{"pid":"d14c70380c35a4313cbbb0acb219fba455f377fd","tid":541662,"uid":5408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6ee63efad8522846fa370fe10f9da9769a14d0","tid":541662,"uid":156986,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"講岀來有無打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得利記既球員先配得起巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9363ca5dba5a99126fc358752ba57643e7ddc4e6","tid":541662,"uid":154585,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曼聯中場連格今季奠定了正選席位，今季英超上陣20場轟入7球，表現令人眼前一亮。前曼聯助教梅倫史甸（Rene Meulensteen）最近披露，雲尼斯達羅以及科蘭都當年都對連格讚譽有加，又形容對方是「英格蘭恩尼斯達」！<br />\n<br />\n對於連格當年還在青年軍受訓的情形，梅倫史甸說：「這令我想起雲尼斯達羅以及<span style=\"color: red;\">科蘭</span>當時來觀看訓練的情形，當他們見到連格時都異口同聲說『天呀！這孩子好出色！』」<br />\n<br />\n梅倫史甸又拿巴塞球星恩尼斯達與連格比較：「我從他們的比賽中看到，兩人的打法好多相似的地方。我相信連格就是『英格蘭恩尼斯達』。我覺得你可以叫他加盟巴塞，然後打恩尼斯達的位置，他一定能夠勝任。他在英超能夠做到，而英超比西甲難打，絕對要看高一線。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問下科蘭係咪真係有講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a7ac66fe20874470832d797e63492a1bafc76a","tid":541662,"uid":319,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"Liniesta<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f68b413aa6a9d2fa30184d361926e9d9025857","tid":541662,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4a7ac66fe20874470832d797e63492a1bafc76a","tid":541662,"uid":319,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"Liniesta<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"Messe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26e15db170f118edc45df590d4df50711abecfe","tid":541662,"uid":14872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T21:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e42e3dc3098f65fb74373c1b44d3d78d097a3a","tid":541662,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T21:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6e4bbb666f79402c5faf409b3898be4b476dde","tid":541662,"uid":65298,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6c6ee63efad8522846fa370fe10f9da9769a14d0","tid":541662,"uid":156986,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"講岀來有無打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/3